        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12">
                <div class="about-inner">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col s12 m4 l5">
                            <div class="about-inner-left">
                                <img class="profile-img" src="~/Images/portfolio/CV_img.jpeg" alt="Profile Image">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col s12 m8 l7">
                            <div class="about-inner-right">
                                <h3>About Me</h3>
                                <p>Hi! Welcome to my portfolio. I'm Tarlan Muradli. I study at Azerbaijan State Oil and Industiry University, 3rd course. I'm interested in Cyber Security, Big Data, Web Development and Linux Administration.</p>
